author: Hannah Sampson
title: Two passengers dead on Coral Princess cruise ship, captain says - Washington Post
description: The coronavirus-hit Coral Princess changed its arrival plans and arrived in Miami on Saturday morning. Two passengers have died, the captain announced.
content:
Two people on the Coral Princess cruise ship, which reported 12 positive cases of coronavirus on Thursday, died overnight, according to an announcement from the ships captain Saturday morning.
